    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A form of ethyl alcohol that through direct distillation creates a constant-boiling-point mixture that is subsequently dehydrated to create absolute alcohol. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
